          "instruction": "Answer the questions based on the audio.",
          "prompt_html": "<h1>MULTIPLE CHOICE 12</h1><p><strong>Questions 15 - 20</strong></p><p>For each question, choose <strong>THREE</strong> correct options.</p><p>Write them in any order in answer boxes <strong>15 - 20</strong>.</p><p><strong>Joining the Sports Centre</strong></p><p>Which THREE are necessary in order to join the sports centre as a student member?</p><p>15</p><p>16</p><p>17</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong></th><th>Full-time or part-time student status</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong></td><td>Proof of being a member of the Students' Union</td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong></td><td>A credit card</td></tr><tr><td><strong>D</strong></td><td>A completed application form</td></tr><tr><td><strong>E</strong></td><td>£20</td></tr><tr><td><strong>F</strong></td><td>Passport photos</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Which THREE are true of the sports centre?</p><p>18</p><p>19</p><p>20</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong></th><th>Access is permitted to members at any point within opening hours.</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong></td><td>Members are not required to bring their membership cards.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong></td><td>There is no fee for replacement membership cards.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>D</strong></td><td>Courts can be booked only by going to the centre.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>E</strong></td><td>The sports centre is open every day of the week.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>F</strong></td><td>The sports centre has different opening hours on Saturday.</td></tr></tbody></table>",
